# 5) Tạo service systemd cho bot admin

Tạo file:

```bash
nano /etc/systemd/system/changjiang-admin-bot.service
```

Dán:

```ini
[Unit]
Description=Changjiang Admin Bot
After=network.target

[Service]
Type=simple
WorkingDirectory=/root
EnvironmentFile=/root/.env
ExecStart=/root/venv/bin/python /root/admin_bot.py
Restart=always
RestartSec=5
User=root

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
```

Reload và bật:

```bash
systemctl daemon-reload
systemctl enable changjiang-admin-bot
systemctl start changjiang-admin-bot
